------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|A.A. Turusin                          |Irkutsk Oblast                        | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|P.T. Burdukov                         |Kaluga Oblast                         | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|G.T. Dyudyayev                        |Kemerovo Oblast                       | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|V.V. Gukov                            |Kursk Oblast                          | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|Yu.V. Sokolov                         |Leningrad Oblast                      | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|N.M. Kharitonov                       |Novosibirsk Oblast                    | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|A.A. Chernyshev                       |Orenburg Oblast                       | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|M.A. Putilov                          |Perm Oblast                           | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
