Article   Type:CSO 

  [Editorial report] Moscow MIROVAYA EKONOMIKA I 
MEZHDUNARODNYYE OTNOSHENIYA in Russian publishes, as a "special 
supplement" to the journal, signed to press 21 December 1993, 
the 333-page 15,000-word "abridged translation from English" of 
the Stockholm International Peace Research Institute's [SIPRI] 
1993 yearbook, "World Armaments and Disarmament." 

</TEXT>

